Understanding of various testing methodologies and SDLC&lt;br&gt;
Understanding of Android/iOS specific technologies and challenges&lt;br&gt;
Experience working in/familiarity with an Agile environment&lt;br&gt;
Up-to-date knowledge of latest Android/iOS devices in the market&lt;br&gt;
Strong communication skills and experience collaborating with multiple groups&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;【About Company】&lt;br&gt;
